column2: SELECT    m.objid, m.ra1 AS ra1, m.dec1 AS dec1,    n.objid, petroRad_u, petroRadErr_u, petroRad_g, petroRadErr_g, petroRad_r, petroRadErr_r, petroRad_i,    petroRadErr_i, petroRad_z, petroRadErr_z, modelMag_u, modelMagErr_u, modelMag_g, modelMagErr_g, modelMag_r, modelMagErr_r,   modelMag_i, modelMagErr_i, modelMag_z, modelMagErr_z,   o.ra AS ra2, o.dec AS dec2 into mydb.final_petro from MyDB.final_# AS m     CROSS APPLY dbo.fGetNearestObjEq (m.ra1, m.dec1, #) AS n     JOIN PhotoObjAll AS o ON n.objid=o.objid
